{"tid":2354122,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"眼帯の喰種(喰種哥)速入，有緊要事情搵您","createTime":"2021-01-05T08:32:15.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T09:46:51.000Z","uid":73381,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"51105e3ab2d7de7a32f74454691caf2bf1361e01","tid":2354122,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:32:15.000Z","msg":"大雞樂死雞樂果班全部熱狗嚟  佢地自己私底下有交換contact<br />\n<br />\n老帽未被人放毒放到上晒腦嘅時候，有同我講過佢同波台友交換過contact。<br />\n<br />\n後尾因為某啲事我想搵返「大雞樂」呢個名係代表邊一位熱狗區議員時(應該係大埔區嘅黃兆建，Google大雞樂就會見到)，先發現老帽原來係貼bam圖前七至八個月已經係大埔去咗搵大雞樂/其他波台熱狗(佢係個po問家陣行過去搵佢地得唔得)，先至發覺可能係果時已經交換咗contact。<br />\n<br />\n佢地應該有group講到明想推邊個Po就推邊個Po。<br />\n<br />\n連囝如果有辦法睇返被削除用户資料，我可以同佢講返上面啲野邊到搵到。"},{"pid":"88531d1569b3efa64ddce0014ac0c095af30cc88","tid":2354122,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:32:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20e66f3ab7b394812b47365483574a22a8648ee9","tid":2354122,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"大雞樂啫係黃兆建呀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大雞樂好似真係區議員黎<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2341380\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2341380</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大埔 group 有藍絲話黃兆健派美心月餅，事實當然唔係咁樣啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2225512\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2225512</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n(上面第二個洗白Po仲要見到老帽痴咗埋去班熱狗堆 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n之前仲要出Po屌過龍門再扮無事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f96784c9fa03c78a29098a53288f882779759719","tid":2354122,"uid":23655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:32:36.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"e91fb6936b69ce7e6ea7dcd2d8a0447c06ce1525","tid":2354122,"uid":73381,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:33:01.000Z","msg":"喰種哥幫推上熱門！等多啲人知呢條友係熱狗黎"},{"pid":"40286771a210be56102ac4dc28bea507caaebc2e","tid":2354122,"uid":199081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auqZwNt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauqZwNt.gif&h=8544057d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"afe3a7205b507a61dc73331761a8f66631ea206a","tid":2354122,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40286771a210be56102ac4dc28bea507caaebc2e","tid":2354122,"uid":199081,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:33:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/auqZwNt.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FauqZwNt.gif&h=8544057d&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-05T08:34:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jppBwXE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjppBwXE.png&h=da31052c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d69227320dfb91a52f18dd0165959fd18a0d295a","tid":2354122,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"afe3a7205b507a61dc73331761a8f66631ea206a","tid":2354122,"uid":73381,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"40286771a210be56102ac4dc28b